INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("119","1","2015-07-02 15:27:25","2015-07-02 15:27:25","[full_width][custom_title]We are all unique, due to our genes[/custom_title][two_third first=\"yes\"]\n\n<strong>Although more than 99,9% of human DNA is identical among all people, it’s the  remaining 0,1% that makes us each unique.</strong>\n\nThe  most  common  type  of  variation  is  called  SNP  (single  nucleotide  polymorphism): <strong> a  SNP may  lead  to  a  change, positive  or  negative, in the  efficiency  or the  functionality  of  all  the biological systems of our body.</strong>\n\nScience have demonstrated that these small differences, taken together, determine the way in which the exposure to multiple environmental factors affects your body, your health, and the aging concerns you’re fighting.\n\nThe  reading  of  SNPs and  their  correlation with  the  environment  makes it  possible  to  identify <strong>specific pathways of personalized  treatment.</strong>\n\n[/two_third][one_third]\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-148\" src=\"http://192.185.139.35/~iddna/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/single-nucleotide-polymorphism-snp.jpg\" alt=\"single-nucleotide-polymorphism-snp\" width=\"306\" height=\"340\" />\n\n[/one_third]\n\n[spacer]\n\n[/full_width]\n\n[full_width background_color=\"#151515\" text_color=\"#888888\"]\n\n[spacer]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">GENETICS CREATES A NEW CLASS OF ANTI-AGING TECHNOLOGY.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>THE LUXURY OF A BESPOKE ANTI-AGING PROGRAM BASED ON YOUR GENETIC CODE</strong>\n<strong> BECAUSE YOUR GENES DON’T LIE …</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[spacer]</p>\n[/full_width]\n\n[full_width background_color=\"#000000\" text_color=\"#ffffff\"][spacer][spacer]\n\n[custom_title]DNA-PERSONALIZED ANTI-AGING, explore iDDNA<sup>®</sup>[/custom_title]\n\nNO MORE GUESSWORK\n\n<strong>We replaced anti-aging guesswork with GENETICALLY-DESIGNED cosmeceuticals OTC (over-the-counter) and nutrico