lication in a peer-reviewed scientific journal. Suisse Life Science may also include your information in Aggregated Genetic and Self-Reported Information disclosed to third-party non-profit and/or commercial research partners who will not publish that information in a peer-reviewed scientific journal. Suisse Life Science will never release your individual-level Genetic Information and/or Self-Reported Information to any third party without asking for and receiving your explicit consent to do so, unless required by law. Further, you acknowledge and agree that Suisse Life Science is free to preserve and disclose any and all Personal Information to law enforcement agencies or others if required to do so by law or in the good faith belief that such preservation or disclosure is reasonably necessary to: (a) comply with legal process (such as a judicial proceeding, court order, or government inquiry) or obligations that Suisse Life Science may owe pursuant to ethical and other professional rules, laws, and regulations; (b) enforce the Suisse Life Science TOS; (c) respond to claims that any content violates the rights of third parties; or (d) protect the rights, property, or personal safety of Suisse Life Science, its employees, its users, its clients, and the public. In such event we will notify you through the contact information you have provided to us in advance, unless doing so would violate the law or a court order. You understand that the technical processing and transmission of the Services, including your Personal Information, may involve (a) transmissions over various networks; and (b) changes to conform and adapt to technical requirements of connecting networks, or devices. Finally, Suisse Life Science may, in its sole discretion, restrict access to the website for any reason.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Please refer to our Privacy Statement to read about data protection related to your information. See our complete <a href=\"https://www.23andme.com/about/privacy/\">Privacy Statement</a> here.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"8\">\r\n	<li><strong>Limited License</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You acknowledge that all User Content, whether publicly posted or privately transmitted, is the sole responsibility of the person from which such User Content originated. This means that you, and not Suisse Life Science, are entirely responsible for all User Content that you upload, post, email, or otherwise transmit via the Service.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You acknowledge that the Services content presented to you as part of the Services, whether original Suisse Life Science Services content or sponsored content within the Services, is protected by copyright and/or other intellectual property rights that are owned by Suisse Life Science and/or the sponsors who provide that content to Suisse Life Science (or by other persons or companies on their behalf). Suisse Life Science grants you a Limited License to copy and distribute free of charge, for non-commercial purposes only, any of the Services content with the exception of content from \"MD\'s Perspectives\" in the \"For the Experts\" section of the website and any other content marked as not subject to this Limited License on the website, provided you: (i) provide the Services content as it appears on the Suisse Life Science website with no changes including but not limited to presenting selections which might tend to misrepresent the substance of the Services content; (ii) include the following attribution on the first page of any materials you distribute: © Suisse Life Science S.A. 2014-2015. All rights reserved; distributed pursuant to a Limited License from Suisse Life Science; (iii) agree you have no right to offer anyone else any further right with respect to this Services content. Aside from the Limited License provided in this paragraph, you may not modify, rent, lease, loan, sell, distribute, or