INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("146","1","2015-06-04 13:37:57","2015-06-04 13:37:57","<h1>DNA-personalized anti-aging</h1>\r\n<strong>We are all unique, due to our genes.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Although more than 99,9% of human DNA is identical among all</strong><strong> people, it’s the  remai</strong><strong>ning 0,1% that makes us each unique.</strong>\r\n\r\nThe  most  common  type  of  variation  is  called  SNP  (single  nucleotide  polymorphism):  <strong>a  SNP may  lead  to  a  change, positive  or  negative, in the  efficiency  or the  functionality  of  all  the biological systems of our body.</strong>\r\n\r\nScience have demonstrated that these small differences, taken together, determine the way in which the exposure to multiple environmental factors affects your body, your health, and the aging concerns you’re fighting.\r\n\r\nThe  reading  of  SNPs and  their  correlation with  the  environment  makes it  possible  to  identify <strong>specific pathways of personalized  treatment</strong>.<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\nGENETICS CREATES A NEW CLASS OF ANTI-AGING TECHNOLOGY.<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>THE LUXURY  OF A BESPOKE ANTI-AGING PROGRAM BASED ON YOUR GENETIC CODE</strong><strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>BECAUSE YOUR GENES DON’T LIE …</strong>\r\n<h2>DNA-PERSONALIZED ANTI-AGING, explore [iD]DNA®</h2>\r\nNO MORE GUESSWORK.\r\n\r\n<strong>We replaced anti-aging guesswork with GENETICALLY-DESIGNED cosmeceuticals OTC (over-the-counter) and nutricosmetics supplements.</strong><strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>The great innovation of the </strong>[<strong>iD</strong>]<strong>DNA®</strong> <strong>ultra-custom</strong> program <strong>is that the genetic guidance permits to adjust the right treatment, the correct dosage, and the best frequency according to your organism’s needs.</strong>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://192.185.139.35/~iddna/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/4.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-113\" src=\"http://192.185.139.35/~iddna/w