INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("162","1","2015-07-14 13:39:14","2015-07-14 13:39:14","<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-65\" src=\"http://192.185.139.35/~iddna/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/flag.png\" alt=\"flag\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Suisse Life Science is a leading LIFESTYLE GENETICS, BIOINFORMATICS and PERSONALIZED LIFE SCIENCE SOLUTIONS company</strong>, with a focus on empowering individuals to identify, control or reverse, potential beauty, lifestyle and age issues long before they appear\n\nLifestyle genetics and bioinformatics are specialist fields that involves genetic sequencing, collecting and analysing the relationship between personal genetic information and biological data. By providing healthcare professional with a deeper understanding of how their clients’ body functions at a genetic and molecular level, we believe we can help them live a better life.\n\nBy analysing an individual’s genetics and lifestyle, we build a personal profile: not just data, but comprehensive reliable actionable personal information. This information is used to create a customized preventative anti-aging program, which addresses the unique challenges of each individual’s situation. \n\niDDNA<sup>®</sup>, our proprietary platform, is the first DNA-PERSONALIZED ANTI-AGING solution to address the root causes of aging.\n\n<strong>More than 5,000,000 PUBLISHED STUDIES ON DNA\n1 ANTI-AGING PROGRAM THAT PUTS THE SCIENCE TO WORK</strong>\n\nDesigned and developed in Switzerland.\n\nOur mission is to establish long-term, effective commercial partnerships with professionals, entepreneurs and organizations worldwide to develop and market research-based life science personalized programs, with our <strong>GENETIC APPROACH TO ANTI-AGING SCIENCE.</strong>\n\nSuisse Life Science is headquartered in Switzerland, with subsidiaries in the U.S. and direct presence in Dubai (MENA region), Hong Kong and Taiwan (APAC region).\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><