INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("384","1","2015-06-29 15:03:36","2015-06-29 15:03:36","[full_width background_color=\"#000000\" text_color=\"#ffffff\"]\r\n\r\n[two_third first=\"yes\"]\r\n\r\nWe  are  all different,  both  physically  and  genetically,  and  we  are  different  in  the  way  that we respond to anti-aging procedures, nutrition and exercise. Some of these differences are due to our  lifestyle  and  the  environment  we  live  in,  but  recent  scientific  advances  have  shown  that VARIATIONS IN OUR DNA ALSO HAVE A BIG PART TO PLAY.\r\n\r\n<strong>Although you can’t change your genetics, science now has proven you can dramatically change how your genes affect your beauty, health &amp; fitness.</strong>\r\n\r\nYou can now experience your own DNA-PERSONALIZED program with an easy 20-mins consultation.\r\n\r\nThis  pioneering  genetic  service  provides  you  with  the  specific  knowledge  to  choose:  your genes play a big part, but looking better for your age or improving your sport potential has no magic  shortcut,  it is a long-standing  process  that  requires  your active  participation and the faithful adjustment to lifestyle, nutrition, supplementation and training  recommendations.\r\n\r\n[/two_third][one_third]\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-239\" src=\"http://192.185.139.35/~iddna/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/portrait-small.jpg\" alt=\"portrait-small\" width=\"270\" height=\"410\" />\r\n\r\n[/one_third]\r\n\r\n[spacer]\r\n\r\n[/full_width]\r\n\r\n[full_width background_color=\"#151515\" text_color=\"#888888\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">GENETICS CREATES A NEW CLASS OF ANTI-AGING TECHNOLOGY.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>THE LUXURY OF A BESPOKE ANTI-AGING PROGRAM BASED ON YOUR GENETIC CODE</strong>\r\n<strong> BECAUSE YOUR GENES DON’T LIE …</strong></p>\r\n[/full_width]\r\n\r\n[full_width background_color=\"#000000\" text_color=\"#ffffff\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[custom_title][iD]DNA® is ALL THE INFORMATION\r\nBEHIND WHAT YOU CAN SEE IN THE MIRROR[/custom_title]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[custom_width width=\"430\"]\r\n\r\nNO MORE TRIAL AND ERROR\r\nTraditional medicine often goes by rule of thumb.\r\n\r\n<strong>[iD]DNA® is a platform technology that addresses the root causes of aging.</strong>\r\n\r\nSCIENCE YOU CAN BELIEVE IN.\r\nRESULTS YOU CAN SEE.\r\n\r\n[/custom_width]\r\n\r\n[/full_width]\r\n\r\n[full_width background_color=\"#000000\" text_color=\"#ffffff\" text_size=\"14\"]\r\n\r\nDNA AND AGE MANAGEMENT\r\n\r\nResearch shows that there are 2 different types of aging:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>INTRINSIC (INTERNAL) AGING, aging caused by the genes we inherit</li>\r\n	<li>EXTRINSIC (EXTERNAL) AGING, aging caused by environmental factors, such as exposure to the sun’s rays.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nINTRINSIC AGING, the natural aging process, is a continuous process that normally begins in our mid-20s.\r\n\r\nYour DNA is the code containing all the information necessary to your cells to develop over time. In an optimal scenario, your cells mantain a perfect balance between the activity and restorative periods, and this enables them to recover from external aggressions, free radicals damage and keep their metabolic functions in order.\r\n\r\nGENES AND AGING\r\n\r\nThe DNA damage theory of aging proposes that aging is a consequence of unrepaired  accumulation of naturally occurring DNA damages. Nuclear DNA damage can contribute to aging either indirectly (by increasing apoptosis or cellular senescence) or directly (by increasing cell dysfunction).\r\n\r\nDNA damages that are naturally occurring, due to normal cellular processes that produce reactive oxygen species, the hydrolytic activities of cellular water, etc., Several inherited genetic defects in ability to repair DNA damage give rise to premature aging suggesting a causal relationship between DNA damage and aging.\r\n\r\nYOUR BIO-AGE\r\n\r\nWith just a saliva sample, we can accurately predict a person\'s age without knowing anything else about them.\r\nUCLA scientists looked at a process called methylation, a chemical modification of one of the four building blocks that make up our DNA. While genes partly shape how our body ages, environmental influences also can change our DNA as we age.\r\n\r\nYOUR BIO-AGE\r\n\r\nTelomeres are a compound structure of unique DNA repeats (TTAGGG) that acts as a protective cap at the end of each strand of DNA. Shortens over time due to aging and lifestyle factors (poor nutrition, psychological stress, lack of exercise, etc.), leaving the DNA that makes up our genes vulnerable to damage.\r\n\r\nYour [iD]DNA® index is an easy-to-understand score to help your [iD]DNA®-certified specialist to caliber the adjustment of your individual treatment and your required active participation for the best possible outcome. Your [iD]DNA® ultra-custom program is personalized according to your [iD]DNA® index.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247\" src=\"http://192.185.139.35/~iddna/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/iddna-diagram.png\" alt=\"iddna-diagram\" width=\"987\" height=\"359\" />\r\n\r\n[/full_width]\r\n\r\n[full_width background_color=\"#000000\" text_color=\"#ffffff\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">GENETICS\r\n+\r\nScience of [DNA] f(x)™\r\n=\r\n<strong>[iD]DNA® ultra-custom biologically active treatments</strong></p>\r\n<strong>The great innovation of the [iD]DNA® ultra-custom program is that the genetic guidance permits to adjust the right treatment, the correct dosage, and the best frequency according to your organism’s needs.</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/full_width]\r\n\r\n[full_width background_color=\"#151515\" text_color=\"#888888\" text_size=\"24\"]\r\n\r\n[custom_width width=\"570\"]\r\n\r\n[one_half first=\"yes\"]\r\n\r\n<strong>Specific deficits.</strong>\r\n<strong>Individual benefits.</strong>\r\n<strong>PRECISION ANTI-AGING</strong>\r\n\r\n[/one_half][one_half]<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-251\" src=\"http: