ccurately predict a person\'s age without knowing anything else about them.\r\nUCLA scientists looked at a process called methylation, a chemical modification of one of the four building blocks that make up our DNA. While genes partly shape how our body ages, environmental influences also can change our DNA as we age.\r\n\r\nYOUR BIO-AGE\r\n\r\nTelomeres are a compound structure of unique DNA repeats (TTAGGG) that acts as a protective cap at the end of each strand of DNA. Shortens over time due to aging and lifestyle factors (poor nutrition, psychological stress, lack of exercise, etc.), leaving the DNA that makes up our genes vulnerable to damage.\r\n\r\nYour [iD]DNA® index is an easy-to-understand score to help your [iD]DNA®-certified specialist to caliber the adjustment of your individual treatment and your required active participation for the best possible outcome. Your [iD]DNA® ultra-custom program is personalized according to your [iD]DNA® index.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-247\" src=\"http://192.185.139.35/~iddna/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/iddna-diagram.png\" alt=\"iddna-diagram\" width=\"987\" height=\"359\" />\r\n\r\n[/full_width]\r\n\r\n[full_width background_color=\"#000000\" text_color=\"#ffffff\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">GENETICS\r\n+\r\nScience of [DNA] f(x)™\r\n=\r\n<strong>[iD]DNA® ultra-custom biologically active treatments</strong></p>\r\n<strong>The great innovation of the [iD]DNA® ultra-custom program is that the genetic guidance permits to adjust the right treatment, the correct dosage, and the best frequency according to your organism’s needs.</strong>\r\n\r\n[/full_width]\r\n\r\n[full_width background_color=\"#151515\" text_color=\"#888888\" text_size=\"24\"]\r\n\r\n[custom_width width=\"570\"]\r\n\r\n[one_half first=\"yes\"]\r\n\r\n<strong>Specific deficits.</strong>\r\n<strong>Individual benefits.</strong>\r\n<strong>PRECISION ANTI-AGING</strong>\r\n\r\n[/one_half][one_half]<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-251\" src=\"http://192.185.139.35/~iddna/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/icon.png\" alt=\"icon\" width=\"185\" height=\"185\" />[/one_half]\r\n\r\n[/custom_width]\r\n\r\n[/full_width]\r\n\r\n[full_width background_color=\"#000000\" text_color=\"#ffffff\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[custom_title]NO MORE GUESSWORK\r\nNo more buying products that feel like they might help[/custom_title]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>We replaced anti-aging guesswork with GENETICALLY-DESIGNED cosmeceuticals OTC (over-the-counter) and nutricosmetics supplements.</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[big_icon_list icon_url=\"http://192.185.139.35/~iddna/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/cruz.png\" text_color=\"#189fc8\" text_size=\"18\"]<strong>PATENTED SCIENCE</strong>\r\n<strong>PROPRIETARY FORMULATIONS</strong>[/big_icon_list]</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">SCIENTIFICALLY FORMULATED from researchers for targeted efficacy,<strong> to protect your genomic integrity and fight:</strong></p>\r\n[custom_width width=\"470\"][special_list type=\"check\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>chrono-aging</li>\r\n	<li>photo-aging</li>\r\n	<li>technological aging (aging caused by mobile phones, iphones, ipads, computers …)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/special_list][/custom_width]\r\n\r\n[/full_width]\r\n\r\n[full_width background_color=\"#000000\" text_color=\"#ffffff\" text_size=\"36\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>REAL SCIENCE.</strong>\r\n<strong>REAL RESULTS.</strong></p>\r\n[/full_width]","[iD]DNA®","","inherit","open","open","","102-revision-v1","","","2015-06-29 15:06:22","2015-06-29 15:06:22","","102","http://192.185.139.35/~iddna/2015/06/29/102-revision-v1/","0","revision","","0");
